### مخطط تدفق النظام (Activity Diagram)

```mermaid
graph TD
    %% بداية الرسمة
    Start(( )) --> OpenApp[User opens Smart Trainer app]
    
    OpenApp --> Login[User logs in or signs up]
    
    Login --> AuthDecision{Is user authenticated?}
    
    AuthDecision -- No --> Error[Show error]
    Error --> Login
    
    AuthDecision -- Yes --> StartSession[User starts exercise session]
    
    StartSession --> Capture[User uploads or captures exercise image]
    
    %% خطوات المعالجة (التي كانت في خانة Model)
    Capture --> Detect[System detects pose landmarks]
    Detect --> Classify[System classifies posture]
    Classify --> Evaluate[System evaluates posture and calculates angles]
    
    %% خطوات التغذية الراجعة
    Evaluate --> Feedback[System generates real-time feedback]
    
    Feedback --> HRDecision{Is heart rate sensor connected?}
    
    HRDecision -- Yes --> BPM[Read BPM and display]
    BPM --> Results[System shows feedback and results]
    
    HRDecision -- No --> Results
    
    Results --> EndSession[User ends the session]
    EndSession --> End(( ))
    
    %% تنسيق الألوان لجعلها تبدو احترافية (اختياري)
    style Start fill:#000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style End fill:#000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style AuthDecision fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style HRDecision fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
